gmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc958b1190d664bc083dd2668d58b6f300af779","tid":1462663,"uid":249187,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:09:09.000Z","msg":"琴日我地目的唔係阻人上機 係文宣啊！<br />\n琴日多人所以癱瘓機場係bonus黎，大家keep住多人就會癱瘓到，唔好阻人上機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地已經唔夠正苦力量大，我地一定要爭取國際間既支持！新聞有報有外國人翻唔到屋企好嬲好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阻人搭lift等會令外國旅客覺得好似俾人玩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 翻到自己國家仲點同我地宣傳<br />\nBTW點樣都唔割席，有咩做得唔好就一齊做翻好"},{"pid":"69c833e362a97368f41bec78424b8fc7587dca42","tid":1462663,"uid":124932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:12:25.000Z","msg":"阻到既話就只可以靠文宣<br />\n<br />\n點知係咪有人扮示威者阻人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你811做得出，你機場都做得架啦<br />\n你點證明佢地唔係先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02352846a3df55e6a913c8d6dfad1c023423798","tid":1462663,"uid":1102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc2292788e8ae5508a367bac056d378e697a28c5","tid":1462663,"uid":140559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99715964d47b5d3296c13dcfa86b9a1ca96b755c","tid":1462663,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:13:34.000Z","msg":"文宣入，以備不時之需"},{"pid":"b11acedcc63ca1b1fedf424962ca457fcd47da3f","tid":1462663,"uid":161121,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:13:55.000Z","msg":"咪撚分化啦！投乜撚呀"},{"pid":"bcd1d12a6cfd98e42ddc7323624f7b2aef6b561d","tid":1462663,"uid":7223,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"258e9a26399205c3f70a7bf39045f0de0703d8df","tid":1462663,"uid":121546,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:07:58.000Z","msg":"第一次塞鐵之後已經大把人發覺冇效果+影響唔到政府